T02TD1639E:267a-0: @267a * // dpal he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa la bstod ba bzhugs /
T02TD1639E:267a-2: * // rgyal ba'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1639E:267a-3: sku mdog sngon po cher 'bar ba'i //
T02TD1639E:267a-4: 'jigs byed mche ba gtsigs pa po //
T02TD1639E:267a-5: g-yas ser g-yon ljang rgyab zhal dkar //
T02TD1639E:267a-6: mnyam med sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1639E:267b-0: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi bdag / rigs btsun @267b rig ma mgul nas 'khyud //
T02TD1639E:267b-1: dbu la rigs kyi bdag po bzhugs //
T02TD1639E:267b-2: bde chen sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1639E:267b-3: sgeg dang dpa' byad 'jigs su rung //
T02TD1639E:267b-4: drag dang dgod dang 'jigs par byed //
T02TD1639E:267b-5: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la //
T02TD1639E:267b-6: nyams dgu yon tan khyod la 'dud //
T02TD1639E:267b-7: nam mkha'i 'od kyis khebs mdzad cing //
T02TD1639E:267b-9: phyag rgya lnga yis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1639E:267b-10: bde gshegs sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1639E:267b-11: g-yas g-yon dang po mda' dang gzhu //
T02TD1639E:267b-13: mgo phreng brgya phyed do shal byas //
T02TD1639E:267b-14: mgon po khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1639E:267b-15: dbu skra kham pa gyen du bsgreng //
T02TD1639E:267b-16: ka p'a la lngas dbu la brgyan //
T02TD1639E:267b-17: na ra stong g-yogs stag lpags bsnams //
T02TD1639E:267b-19: dngos po'i rang bzhin kun gyi mchog / sku la mtshan dang dpe byad rdzogs //
T02TD1639E:267b-20: 'gro ba'i don ni mdzad pa po //
T02TD1639E:267b-21: sku gsum bdag nyid khyod la 'dud //
T02TD1639E:267b-22: khyod kyi ye shes spyan zur gyis //
T02TD1639E:267b-23: mi mthun phyogs rnams skrag mdzad cing //
T02TD1639E:267b-24: rgyal mtshan dril bus slar gso mdzad //
T02TD1639E:267b-26: sku gsum ye shes lnga bdag nyid //
T02TD1639E:267b-27: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyi gtso //
T02TD1639E:267b-28: 'gro ba'i mi shes gcod pa po //
T02TD1639E:267b-29: stong nyid snying po khyod la 'dud //
T02TD1639E:267b-30: sangs rgyas byang chub sems rnams dang //
T02TD1639E:267b-31: de nyid brtan par g-yo bcas pa //
T02TD1639E:267b-32: khams gsum 'di dag thams cad kyi //
T02TD1639E:267b-33: bdag nyid chen po khyod la 'dud //
T02TD1639E:267b-34: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel byed cing //
T02TD1639E:267b-35: phun sum tshogs pa kun ster pa //
T02TD1639E:267b-36: byang chub lam ni ston pa po //
T02TD1639E:267b-37: ye shes sku khyod phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1639E:267b-38: bsam med dpe dang bral bas brjod du med //
T02TD1639E:267b-39: bde chen sku ste mi 'gyur 'dus ma byas //
T02TD1639E:267b-40: dngos dang dngos med rnam spangs dmigs pa med //
T02TD1639E:267b-41: bde chen rdo rje mkha' 'gro phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1639E:267b-42: shar phyogs lha mo rdo rje'i rigs //
T02TD1639E:267b-43: byams pa'i bdag nyid sku mdog sngo //
T02TD1639E:267b-44: sa khams me long ye shes bdag / rdo rje mkha' 'gro phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1639E:267b-45: lho phyogs lha mo rin chen rigs //
T02TD1639E:267b-46: snying rje'i bdag nyid sku mdog ser //
T02TD1639E:268a-1: nyid ye shes bdag / rin chen mkha' 'gro phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1639E:268a-2: nub phyogs lha mo padma'i rigs //
T02TD1639E:268a-3: dga' ba'i bdag nyid sku mdog dkar //
T02TD1639E:268a-4: me khams so sor rtog rang bzhin //
T02TD1639E:268a-6: byang phyogs lha mo las kyi rigs//
T02TD1639E:268a-7: btang snyoms rang bzhin sku mdog ljang //
T02TD1639E:268a-8: rlung khams bya ba grub rang bzhin //
T02TD1639E:268a-10: thams cad zhal bzhi phyag bzhi ma //
T02TD1639E:268a-11: phyag na rang rang mtshan ma 'dzin //
T02TD1639E:268a-12: mtshan dang dpe byad sku la rdzogs //
T02TD1639E:268a-13: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1639E:268a-15: mi mgo khrag 'dzag do shal byas //
T02TD1639E:268a-16: zhabs gnyis nyi mar phyed krung bzhugs //
T02TD1639E:268a-18: phyag rgya rnam pa lnga dang ldan //
T02TD1639E:268a-19: ka p'a la lngas dbu la brgyan //
T02TD1639E:268a-20: sgeg pa la sogs nyams dang ldan //
T02TD1639E:268a-22: rje btsun 'khor dang bcas pa la //
T02TD1639E:268a-23: bdag gis bstod pa'i bsod nams kyis //
T02TD1639E:268a-24: sems can kun gyis rje btsun gyi //
T02TD1639E:268a-25: go 'phang bla med thob par shog / rje btsun dpal he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa'i bstod pa rdzogs so//
